{"tid":2214990,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登大戰] 特斯拉起訴特朗普政府，要求停止對華關税","createTime":"2020-09-23T15:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T00:42:50.000Z","uid":108201,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"30855744c66f0decdeb1e95c8414d5ef42edd1f9","tid":2214990,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T15:50:30.000Z","msg":"好多連登仔賺過Tesla錢，屌，Tesla奶共架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n據美國彭博社9月23日報道，美國電動汽車製造商特斯拉週一在美國紐約的國際貿易法院，對美國特朗普當局提起訴訟，以阻止後者對特斯拉從中國進口的物品徵收新的關税。<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">特斯拉希望法庭能夠裁定特朗普當局的做法非法，並讓其退還特斯拉已經支付的款項，包括利息。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n來源：Bloomberg"},{"pid":"1203924003213126ca456fc252e4e4b7d27bb123","tid":2214990,"uid":24306,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T15:53:14.000Z","msg":"支那股<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />QQ有份"},{"pid":"aa53dbaff5c271cb8b791847f675f991931e0fb1","tid":2214990,"uid":2300,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T16:04:22.000Z","msg":"奶共 預左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 走鬼先"},{"pid":"4b5aad562c373c0c36f5f459410e15953417f519","tid":2214990,"uid":179825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T17:27:47.000Z","msg":"Tesla會跌到pk"},{"pid":"3d7e8dda5be8c5e0aaf04527890f2de0e0deea35","tid":2214990,"uid":106018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T00:42:50.000Z","msg":"475坐緊<br />\n好唔好盤前放 之後再沽佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}